      "date": "2014-06-26 17:48:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nFailure is sanity/69 LU-5240\nhttps://old-testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/83e942b6-fd11-11e3-9add-52540035b04c",
